FROM [PROYECTO] AS [p]

INNER JOIN [SERVICIOSEJECUCION] AS [s] ON [p].[ID] = [s].[IDPROYECTO]
INNER JOIN [SERVICIOS] AS [s0] ON [s].[IDSERVICIO] = [s0].[ID]
INNER JOIN [CUENTA] AS [c] ON [s0].[IDCUENTA] = [c].[ID]
WHERE ([p].[ID] = @__idproyecto_0) AND ([s].[TIPOSERVICIO] = @__tipo_1)

    WHEN ([s].[ESTADO] <> 'Forecast') OR [s].[ESTADO] IS NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)

SELECT [g].[ID] AS [IdGastosReal], [g].[IDGASTO] AS [IdGasto], [g].[IDPROVEEDOR] AS [IdProveedor], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[ID]
    ELSE 0
END AS [IdSegmento], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[NOMBRE]
    ELSE ''
END AS [NombreSegmento], [c].[CUENTA] AS [Cuenta], [c].[IDCUENTA] AS [IdCuenta], [g].[MONTO] AS [Monto], [g].[FECHA] AS [Fecha], [g].[OBSERVACION] AS [Observacion], [g].[ESTADO] AS [Estado], [g].[VENTA] AS [Venta]
FROM [PROYECTO] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [GASTOSEJECUCION] AS [g] ON [p].[ID] = [g].[IDPROYECTO]
INNER JOIN [GASTOS] AS [g0] ON [g].[IDGASTO] = [g0].[ID]
LEFT JOIN [SEGMENTO] AS [s] ON [g].[SEGMENTO] = [s].[ID]
INNER JOIN [CUENTA] AS [c] ON [g0].[IDCUENTA] = [c].[ID]
WHERE [p].[ID] = @__idproyecto_0
ORDER BY CASE
    WHEN ([g].[ESTADO] <> 'Forecast') OR [g].[ESTADO] IS NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END, [g].[FECHA]

SELECT [g].[ID] AS [IdGastosReal], [g].[IDGASTO] AS [IdGasto], [g].[IDPROVEEDOR] AS [IdProveedor], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[ID]
    ELSE 0
END AS [IdSegmento], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[NOMBRE]
    ELSE ''
END AS [NombreSegmento], [c].[CUENTA] AS [Cuenta], [c].[IDCUENTA] AS [IdCuenta], [g].[MONTO] AS [Monto], [g].[FECHA] AS [Fecha], [g].[OBSERVACION] AS [Observacion], [g].[ESTADO] AS [Estado], [g].[VENTA] AS [Venta]
FROM [PROYECTO] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [GASTOSEJECUCION] AS [g] ON [p].[ID] = [g].[IDPROYECTO]
INNER JOIN [GASTOS] AS [g0] ON [g].[IDGASTO] = [g0].[ID]
LEFT JOIN [SEGMENTO] AS [s] ON [g].[SEGMENTO] = [s].[ID]
INNER JOIN [CUENTA] AS [c] ON [g0].[IDCUENTA] = [c].[ID]
WHERE [p].[ID] = @__idproyecto_0
ORDER BY CASE
    WHEN ([g].[ESTADO] <> 'Forecast') OR [g].[ESTADO] IS NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END, [g].[FECHA]

INNER JOIN [SERVICIOS] AS [s0] ON [s].[IDSERVICIO] = [s0].[ID]

    ELSE 0

    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[NOMBRE]
    ELSE ''
END AS [NombreSegmento], [c].[CUENTA] AS [Cuenta], [c].[IDCUENTA] AS [IdCuenta], [g].[MONTO] AS [Monto], [g].[FECHA] AS [Fecha], [g].[OBSERVACION] AS [Observacion], [g].[ESTADO] AS [Estado], [g].[VENTA] AS [Venta]

INNER JOIN [GASTOS] AS [g0] ON [g].[IDGASTO] = [g0].[ID]

SELECT [p].[ID] AS [idproyecto], [p].[NOMBRE] AS [nombreproyecto], COALESCE([g].[ANIO], 0) AS [anio], COALESCE([g].[MES], 0) AS [mes], [g].[TIPORECURSO] AS [tiporecurso], COALESCE([h].[IDCUENTASOCIO], 0) AS [idcuentasocio], COALESCE([h].[IDCUENTASTAFF], 0) AS [idcuentastaff], [h].[CUENTASOCIO] AS [cuentasocio], [h].[CUENTASTAFF] AS [cuentastaff], COALESCE(SUM(COALESCE([g].[HHTOTALES], 0.0)), 0.0) AS [totalhh], COALESCE(SUM(COALESCE([g].[HHTOTALES], 0.0) * [g].[costounitariomes]), 0.0) AS [costorecursosocio], [h0].[COSTOSOCIO] AS [costohhsocio], [h0].[COSTOSTAFF] AS [costohhstaff], [g].[ID] AS [idgastohh], COALESCE([g].[REAJUSTE], 0.0) AS [reajuste], COALESCE([g].[MONTO], 0.0) AS [monto], [g].[OBSERVACION] AS [observacion], COALESCE([g].[FECHAPAGO], NULL) AS [fechapago], COALESCE([g].[ESTADO], 0) AS [estado], COALESCE([g].[costounitariomes], 0.0) AS [costounitariomes]
FROM [GASTOSHHHEJECUCION] AS [g]
INNER JOIN [PROYECTO] AS [p] ON [g].[IDPROYECTO] = [p].[ID]
INNER JOIN [HISTORIALCUENTASPROYECTO] AS [h] ON [p].[ID] = [h].[IDPROYECTO]
INNER JOIN [HISTORIAL_COSTOS_PROYECTOS] AS [h0] ON [p].[ID] = [h0].[IDPROYECTO]
WHERE ([p].[STATUS_PROYECTO] = 2) AND ([p].[ID] = @__idproyecto_0)
GROUP BY [p].[ID], [p].[NOMBRE], [g].[ID], [g].[ANIO], [g].[MES], [g].[TIPORECURSO], [h].[IDCUENTASOCIO], [h].[IDCUENTASTAFF], [h].[CUENTASOCIO], [h].[CUENTASTAFF], [h0].[COSTOSOCIO], [h0].[COSTOSTAFF], [g].[REAJUSTE], [g].[MONTO], [g].[OBSERVACION], [g].[FECHAPAGO], [g].[ESTADO], [g].[costounitariomes]
ORDER BY COALESCE([g].[ANIO], 0), COALESCE([g].[MES], 0)

    ELSE 0

    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[NOMBRE]
    ELSE ''
END AS [NombreSegmento], [c].[CUENTA] AS [Cuenta], [c].[IDCUENTA] AS [IdCuenta], [g].[MONTO] AS [Monto], [g].[FECHA] AS [Fecha], [g].[OBSERVACION] AS [Observacion], [g].[ESTADO] AS [Estado], [g].[VENTA] AS [Venta]

INNER JOIN [GASTOS] AS [g0] ON [g].[IDGASTO] = [g0].[ID]
LEFT JOIN [SEGMENTO] AS [s] ON [g].[SEGMENTO] = [s].[ID]
INNER JOIN [CUENTA] AS [c] ON [g0].[IDCUENTA] = [c].[ID]

    ELSE ''

INNER JOIN [GASTOS] AS [g0] ON [g].[IDGASTO] = [g0].[ID]
LEFT JOIN [SEGMENTO] AS [s] ON [g].[SEGMENTO] = [s].[ID]
INNER JOIN [CUENTA] AS [c] ON [g0].[IDCUENTA] = [c].[ID]

SELECT [g].[ID] AS [IdGastosReal], [g].[IDGASTO] AS [IdGasto], [g].[IDPROVEEDOR] AS [IdProveedor], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[ID]
    ELSE 0
END AS [IdSegmento], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[NOMBRE]
    ELSE ''
END AS [NombreSegmento], [c].[CUENTA] AS [Cuenta], [c].[IDCUENTA] AS [IdCuenta], [g].[MONTO] AS [Monto], [g].[FECHA] AS [Fecha], [g].[OBSERVACION] AS [Observacion], [g].[ESTADO] AS [Estado], [g].[VENTA] AS [Venta]
FROM [PROYECTO] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [GASTOSEJECUCION] AS [g] ON [p].[ID] = [g].[IDPROYECTO]
INNER JOIN [GASTOS] AS [g0] ON [g].[IDGASTO] = [g0].[ID]
LEFT JOIN [SEGMENTO] AS [s] ON [g].[SEGMENTO] = [s].[ID]
INNER JOIN [CUENTA] AS [c] ON [g0].[IDCUENTA] = [c].[ID]

SELECT [g].[ID] AS [IdGastosReal], [g].[IDGASTO] AS [IdGasto], [g].[IDPROVEEDOR] AS [IdProveedor], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[ID]
    ELSE 0
END AS [IdSegmento], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[NOMBRE]
    ELSE ''
END AS [NombreSegmento], [c].[CUENTA] AS [Cuenta], [c].[IDCUENTA] AS [IdCuenta], [g].[MONTO] AS [Monto], [g].[FECHA] AS [Fecha], [g].[OBSERVACION] AS [Observacion], [g].[ESTADO] AS [Estado], [g].[VENTA] AS [Venta]
FROM [PROYECTO] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [GASTOSEJECUCION] AS [g] ON [p].[ID] = [g].[IDPROYECTO]
INNER JOIN [GASTOS] AS [g0] ON [g].[IDGASTO] = [g0].[ID]
LEFT JOIN [SEGMENTO] AS [s] ON [g].[SEGMENTO] = [s].[ID]
INNER JOIN [CUENTA] AS [c] ON [g0].[IDCUENTA] = [c].[ID]
WHERE [p].[ID] = @__idproyecto_0
ORDER BY CASE
    WHEN ([g].[ESTADO] <> 'Forecast') OR [g].[ESTADO] IS NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END, [g].[FECHA]

SELECT [g].[ID] AS [IdGastosReal], [g].[IDGASTO] AS [IdGasto], [g].[IDPROVEEDOR] AS [IdProveedor], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[ID]
    ELSE 0
END AS [IdSegmento], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[NOMBRE]
    ELSE ''
END AS [NombreSegmento], [c].[CUENTA] AS [Cuenta], [c].[IDCUENTA] AS [IdCuenta], [g].[MONTO] AS [Monto], [g].[FECHA] AS [Fecha], [g].[OBSERVACION] AS [Observacion], [g].[ESTADO] AS [Estado], [g].[VENTA] AS [Venta]
FROM [PROYECTO] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [GASTOSEJECUCION] AS [g] ON [p].[ID] = [g].[IDPROYECTO]
INNER JOIN [GASTOS] AS [g0] ON [g].[IDGASTO] = [g0].[ID]
LEFT JOIN [SEGMENTO] AS [s] ON [g].[SEGMENTO] = [s].[ID]
INNER JOIN [CUENTA] AS [c] ON [g0].[IDCUENTA] = [c].[ID]
WHERE [p].[ID] = @__idproyecto_0
ORDER BY CASE
    WHEN ([g].[ESTADO] <> 'Forecast') OR [g].[ESTADO] IS NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END, [g].[FECHA]

    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[ID]
    ELSE 0
END AS [IdSegmento], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[NOMBRE]
    ELSE ''
END AS [NombreSegmento], [c].[CUENTA] AS [Cuenta], [c].[IDCUENTA] AS [IdCuenta], [g].[MONTO] AS [Monto], [g].[FECHA] AS [Fecha], [g].[OBSERVACION] AS [Observacion], [g].[ESTADO] AS [Estado], [g].[VENTA] AS [Venta]
FROM [PROYECTO] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [GASTOSEJECUCION] AS [g] ON [p].[ID] = [g].[IDPROYECTO]
INNER JOIN [GASTOS] AS [g0] ON [g].[IDGASTO] = [g0].[ID]
LEFT JOIN [SEGMENTO] AS [s] ON [g].[SEGMENTO] = [s].[ID]
INNER JOIN [CUENTA] AS [c] ON [g0].[IDCUENTA] = [c].[ID]
WHERE [p].[ID] = @__idproyecto_0
ORDER BY CASE
    WHEN ([g].[ESTADO] <> 'Forecast') OR [g].[ESTADO] IS NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END, [g].[FECHA]

2025-08-05 14:09:20.964 -04:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (14ms) [Parameters=[@__idproyecto_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [g].[ID] AS [IdGastosReal], [g].[IDGASTO] AS [IdGasto], [g].[IDPROVEEDOR] AS [IdProveedor], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[ID]
    ELSE 0
END AS [IdSegmento], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[NOMBRE]
    ELSE ''
END AS [NombreSegmento], [c].[CUENTA] AS [Cuenta], [c].[IDCUENTA] AS [IdCuenta], [g].[MONTO] AS [Monto], [g].[FECHA] AS [Fecha], [g].[OBSERVACION] AS [Observacion], [g].[ESTADO] AS [Estado], [g].[VENTA] AS [Venta]
FROM [PROYECTO] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [GASTOSEJECUCION] AS [g] ON [p].[ID] = [g].[IDPROYECTO]
INNER JOIN [GASTOS] AS [g0] ON [g].[IDGASTO] = [g0].[ID]
LEFT JOIN [SEGMENTO] AS [s] ON [g].[SEGMENTO] = [s].[ID]
INNER JOIN [CUENTA] AS [c] ON [g0].[IDCUENTA] = [c].[ID]
WHERE [p].[ID] = @__idproyecto_0
ORDER BY CASE
    WHEN ([g].[ESTADO] <> 'Forecast') OR [g].[ESTADO] IS NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END, [g].[FECHA]

SELECT [g].[ID] AS [IdGastosReal], [g].[IDGASTO] AS [IdGasto], [g].[IDPROVEEDOR] AS [IdProveedor], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[ID]
    ELSE 0
END AS [IdSegmento], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[NOMBRE]
    ELSE ''
END AS [NombreSegmento], [c].[CUENTA] AS [Cuenta], [c].[IDCUENTA] AS [IdCuenta], [g].[MONTO] AS [Monto], [g].[FECHA] AS [Fecha], [g].[OBSERVACION] AS [Observacion], [g].[ESTADO] AS [Estado], [g].[VENTA] AS [Venta]
FROM [PROYECTO] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [GASTOSEJECUCION] AS [g] ON [p].[ID] = [g].[IDPROYECTO]
INNER JOIN [GASTOS] AS [g0] ON [g].[IDGASTO] = [g0].[ID]
LEFT JOIN [SEGMENTO] AS [s] ON [g].[SEGMENTO] = [s].[ID]
INNER JOIN [CUENTA] AS [c] ON [g0].[IDCUENTA] = [c].[ID]
WHERE [p].[ID] = @__idproyecto_0
ORDER BY CASE
    WHEN ([g].[ESTADO] <> 'Forecast') OR [g].[ESTADO] IS NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END, [g].[FECHA]

SELECT [g].[ID] AS [IdGastosReal], [g].[IDGASTO] AS [IdGasto], [g].[IDPROVEEDOR] AS [IdProveedor], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[ID]
    ELSE 0
END AS [IdSegmento], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[NOMBRE]
    ELSE ''
END AS [NombreSegmento], [c].[CUENTA] AS [Cuenta], [c].[IDCUENTA] AS [IdCuenta], [g].[MONTO] AS [Monto], [g].[FECHA] AS [Fecha], [g].[OBSERVACION] AS [Observacion], [g].[ESTADO] AS [Estado], [g].[VENTA] AS [Venta]
FROM [PROYECTO] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [GASTOSEJECUCION] AS [g] ON [p].[ID] = [g].[IDPROYECTO]
INNER JOIN [GASTOS] AS [g0] ON [g].[IDGASTO] = [g0].[ID]
LEFT JOIN [SEGMENTO] AS [s] ON [g].[SEGMENTO] = [s].[ID]
INNER JOIN [CUENTA] AS [c] ON [g0].[IDCUENTA] = [c].[ID]
WHERE [p].[ID] = @__idproyecto_0
ORDER BY CASE
    WHEN ([g].[ESTADO] <> 'Forecast') OR [g].[ESTADO] IS NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END, [g].[FECHA]

SELECT [g].[ID] AS [IdGastosReal], [g].[IDGASTO] AS [IdGasto], [g].[IDPROVEEDOR] AS [IdProveedor], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[ID]
    ELSE 0
END AS [IdSegmento], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[NOMBRE]
    ELSE ''
END AS [NombreSegmento], [c].[CUENTA] AS [Cuenta], [c].[IDCUENTA] AS [IdCuenta], [g].[MONTO] AS [Monto], [g].[FECHA] AS [Fecha], [g].[OBSERVACION] AS [Observacion], [g].[ESTADO] AS [Estado], [g].[VENTA] AS [Venta]
FROM [PROYECTO] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [GASTOSEJECUCION] AS [g] ON [p].[ID] = [g].[IDPROYECTO]
INNER JOIN [GASTOS] AS [g0] ON [g].[IDGASTO] = [g0].[ID]
LEFT JOIN [SEGMENTO] AS [s] ON [g].[SEGMENTO] = [s].[ID]
INNER JOIN [CUENTA] AS [c] ON [g0].[IDCUENTA] = [c].[ID]
WHERE [p].[ID] = @__idproyecto_0
ORDER BY CASE
    WHEN ([g].[ESTADO] <> 'Forecast') OR [g].[ESTADO] IS NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END, [g].[FECHA]

SELECT [g].[ID] AS [IdGastosReal], [g].[IDGASTO] AS [IdGasto], [g].[IDPROVEEDOR] AS [IdProveedor], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[ID]
    ELSE 0
END AS [IdSegmento], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[NOMBRE]
    ELSE ''
END AS [NombreSegmento], [c].[CUENTA] AS [Cuenta], [c].[IDCUENTA] AS [IdCuenta], [g].[MONTO] AS [Monto], [g].[FECHA] AS [Fecha], [g].[OBSERVACION] AS [Observacion], [g].[ESTADO] AS [Estado], [g].[VENTA] AS [Venta]
FROM [PROYECTO] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [GASTOSEJECUCION] AS [g] ON [p].[ID] = [g].[IDPROYECTO]
INNER JOIN [GASTOS] AS [g0] ON [g].[IDGASTO] = [g0].[ID]
LEFT JOIN [SEGMENTO] AS [s] ON [g].[SEGMENTO] = [s].[ID]
INNER JOIN [CUENTA] AS [c] ON [g0].[IDCUENTA] = [c].[ID]
WHERE [p].[ID] = @__idproyecto_0
ORDER BY CASE
    WHEN ([g].[ESTADO] <> 'Forecast') OR [g].[ESTADO] IS NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END, [g].[FECHA]

    ELSE ''

    ELSE 0

    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[NOMBRE]
    ELSE ''
END AS [NombreSegmento], [c].[CUENTA] AS [Cuenta], [c].[IDCUENTA] AS [IdCuenta], [g].[MONTO] AS [Monto], [g].[FECHA] AS [Fecha], [g].[OBSERVACION] AS [Observacion], [g].[ESTADO] AS [Estado], [g].[VENTA] AS [Venta]
FROM [PROYECTO] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [GASTOSEJECUCION] AS [g] ON [p].[ID] = [g].[IDPROYECTO]
INNER JOIN [GASTOS] AS [g0] ON [g].[IDGASTO] = [g0].[ID]
LEFT JOIN [SEGMENTO] AS [s] ON [g].[SEGMENTO] = [s].[ID]
INNER JOIN [CUENTA] AS [c] ON [g0].[IDCUENTA] = [c].[ID]
WHERE [p].[ID] = @__idproyecto_0

    WHEN ([g].[ESTADO] <> 'Forecast') OR [g].[ESTADO] IS NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)

2025-08-05 14:37:37.937 -04:00 [INF] Request finished HTTP/2 GET https://localhost:7297/EjecucionProyecto/GetProveedoresServicios - 200 null application/json; charset=utf-8 16.9651ms
2025-08-05 14:37:37.938 -04:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (20ms) [Parameters=[@__idproyecto_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [g].[ID] AS [IdGastosReal], [g].[IDGASTO] AS [IdGasto], [g].[IDPROVEEDOR] AS [IdProveedor], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[ID]
    ELSE 0
END AS [IdSegmento], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[NOMBRE]
    ELSE ''
END AS [NombreSegmento], [c].[CUENTA] AS [Cuenta], [c].[IDCUENTA] AS [IdCuenta], [g].[MONTO] AS [Monto], [g].[FECHA] AS [Fecha], [g].[OBSERVACION] AS [Observacion], [g].[ESTADO] AS [Estado], [g].[VENTA] AS [Venta]
FROM [PROYECTO] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [GASTOSEJECUCION] AS [g] ON [p].[ID] = [g].[IDPROYECTO]
INNER JOIN [GASTOS] AS [g0] ON [g].[IDGASTO] = [g0].[ID]
LEFT JOIN [SEGMENTO] AS [s] ON [g].[SEGMENTO] = [s].[ID]
INNER JOIN [CUENTA] AS [c] ON [g0].[IDCUENTA] = [c].[ID]
WHERE [p].[ID] = @__idproyecto_0
ORDER BY CASE

SELECT [g].[ID] AS [IdGastosReal], [g].[IDGASTO] AS [IdGasto], [g].[IDPROVEEDOR] AS [IdProveedor], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[ID]
    ELSE 0
END AS [IdSegmento], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[NOMBRE]
    ELSE ''
END AS [NombreSegmento], [c].[CUENTA] AS [Cuenta], [c].[IDCUENTA] AS [IdCuenta], [g].[MONTO] AS [Monto], [g].[FECHA] AS [Fecha], [g].[OBSERVACION] AS [Observacion], [g].[ESTADO] AS [Estado], [g].[VENTA] AS [Venta]
FROM [PROYECTO] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [GASTOSEJECUCION] AS [g] ON [p].[ID] = [g].[IDPROYECTO]
INNER JOIN [GASTOS] AS [g0] ON [g].[IDGASTO] = [g0].[ID]
LEFT JOIN [SEGMENTO] AS [s] ON [g].[SEGMENTO] = [s].[ID]
INNER JOIN [CUENTA] AS [c] ON [g0].[IDCUENTA] = [c].[ID]
WHERE [p].[ID] = @__idproyecto_0
ORDER BY CASE
    WHEN ([g].[ESTADO] <> 'Forecast') OR [g].[ESTADO] IS NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END, [g].[FECHA]

SELECT [g].[ID] AS [IdGastosReal], [g].[IDGASTO] AS [IdGasto], [g].[IDPROVEEDOR] AS [IdProveedor], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[ID]
    ELSE 0
END AS [IdSegmento], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[NOMBRE]
    ELSE ''
END AS [NombreSegmento], [c].[CUENTA] AS [Cuenta], [c].[IDCUENTA] AS [IdCuenta], [g].[MONTO] AS [Monto], [g].[FECHA] AS [Fecha], [g].[OBSERVACION] AS [Observacion], [g].[ESTADO] AS [Estado], [g].[VENTA] AS [Venta]
FROM [PROYECTO] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [GASTOSEJECUCION] AS [g] ON [p].[ID] = [g].[IDPROYECTO]
INNER JOIN [GASTOS] AS [g0] ON [g].[IDGASTO] = [g0].[ID]
LEFT JOIN [SEGMENTO] AS [s] ON [g].[SEGMENTO] = [s].[ID]
INNER JOIN [CUENTA] AS [c] ON [g0].[IDCUENTA] = [c].[ID]
WHERE [p].[ID] = @__idproyecto_0
ORDER BY CASE
    WHEN ([g].[ESTADO] <> 'Forecast') OR [g].[ESTADO] IS NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END, [g].[FECHA]

SELECT [g].[ID] AS [IdGastosReal], [g].[IDGASTO] AS [IdGasto], [g].[IDPROVEEDOR] AS [IdProveedor], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[ID]
    ELSE 0
END AS [IdSegmento], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[NOMBRE]
    ELSE ''
END AS [NombreSegmento], [c].[CUENTA] AS [Cuenta], [c].[IDCUENTA] AS [IdCuenta], [g].[MONTO] AS [Monto], [g].[FECHA] AS [Fecha], [g].[OBSERVACION] AS [Observacion], [g].[ESTADO] AS [Estado], [g].[VENTA] AS [Venta]
FROM [PROYECTO] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [GASTOSEJECUCION] AS [g] ON [p].[ID] = [g].[IDPROYECTO]
INNER JOIN [GASTOS] AS [g0] ON [g].[IDGASTO] = [g0].[ID]
LEFT JOIN [SEGMENTO] AS [s] ON [g].[SEGMENTO] = [s].[ID]
INNER JOIN [CUENTA] AS [c] ON [g0].[IDCUENTA] = [c].[ID]
WHERE [p].[ID] = @__idproyecto_0
ORDER BY CASE
    WHEN ([g].[ESTADO] <> 'Forecast') OR [g].[ESTADO] IS NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END, [g].[FECHA]

    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[ID]
    ELSE 0
END AS [IdSegmento], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[NOMBRE]
    ELSE ''
END AS [NombreSegmento], [c].[CUENTA] AS [Cuenta], [c].[IDCUENTA] AS [IdCuenta], [g].[MONTO] AS [Monto], [g].[FECHA] AS [Fecha], [g].[OBSERVACION] AS [Observacion], [g].[ESTADO] AS [Estado], [g].[VENTA] AS [Venta]
FROM [PROYECTO] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [GASTOSEJECUCION] AS [g] ON [p].[ID] = [g].[IDPROYECTO]
INNER JOIN [GASTOS] AS [g0] ON [g].[IDGASTO] = [g0].[ID]
LEFT JOIN [SEGMENTO] AS [s] ON [g].[SEGMENTO] = [s].[ID]
INNER JOIN [CUENTA] AS [c] ON [g0].[IDCUENTA] = [c].[ID]
WHERE [p].[ID] = @__idproyecto_0
ORDER BY CASE
    WHEN ([g].[ESTADO] <> 'Forecast') OR [g].[ESTADO] IS NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END, [g].[FECHA]

SELECT [g].[ID] AS [IdGastosReal], [g].[IDGASTO] AS [IdGasto], [g].[IDPROVEEDOR] AS [IdProveedor], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[ID]
    ELSE 0
END AS [IdSegmento], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[NOMBRE]
    ELSE ''
END AS [NombreSegmento], [c].[CUENTA] AS [Cuenta], [c].[IDCUENTA] AS [IdCuenta], [g].[MONTO] AS [Monto], [g].[FECHA] AS [Fecha], [g].[OBSERVACION] AS [Observacion], [g].[ESTADO] AS [Estado], [g].[VENTA] AS [Venta]
FROM [PROYECTO] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [GASTOSEJECUCION] AS [g] ON [p].[ID] = [g].[IDPROYECTO]
INNER JOIN [GASTOS] AS [g0] ON [g].[IDGASTO] = [g0].[ID]
LEFT JOIN [SEGMENTO] AS [s] ON [g].[SEGMENTO] = [s].[ID]
INNER JOIN [CUENTA] AS [c] ON [g0].[IDCUENTA] = [c].[ID]
WHERE [p].[ID] = @__idproyecto_0
ORDER BY CASE
    WHEN ([g].[ESTADO] <> 'Forecast') OR [g].[ESTADO] IS NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END, [g].[FECHA]

INNER JOIN [HISTORIALCUENTASPROYECTO] AS [h] ON [p].[ID] = [h].[IDPROYECTO]
INNER JOIN [HISTORIAL_COSTOS_PROYECTOS] AS [h0] ON [p].[ID] = [h0].[IDPROYECTO]
WHERE ([p].[STATUS_PROYECTO] = 2) AND ([p].[ID] = @__idproyecto_0)
GROUP BY [p].[ID], [p].[NOMBRE], [g].[ID], [g].[ANIO], [g].[MES], [g].[TIPORECURSO], [h].[IDCUENTASOCIO], [h].[IDCUENTASTAFF], [h].[CUENTASOCIO], [h].[CUENTASTAFF], [h0].[COSTOSOCIO], [h0].[COSTOSTAFF], [g].[REAJUSTE], [g].[MONTO], [g].[OBSERVACION], [g].[FECHAPAGO], [g].[ESTADO], [g].[costounitariomes]
ORDER BY COALESCE([g].[ANIO], 0), COALESCE([g].[MES], 0)

SELECT [g].[ID] AS [IdGastosReal], [g].[IDGASTO] AS [IdGasto], [g].[IDPROVEEDOR] AS [IdProveedor], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[ID]
    ELSE 0
END AS [IdSegmento], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[NOMBRE]
    ELSE ''
END AS [NombreSegmento], [c].[CUENTA] AS [Cuenta], [c].[IDCUENTA] AS [IdCuenta], [g].[MONTO] AS [Monto], [g].[FECHA] AS [Fecha], [g].[OBSERVACION] AS [Observacion], [g].[ESTADO] AS [Estado], [g].[VENTA] AS [Venta]
FROM [PROYECTO] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [GASTOSEJECUCION] AS [g] ON [p].[ID] = [g].[IDPROYECTO]
INNER JOIN [GASTOS] AS [g0] ON [g].[IDGASTO] = [g0].[ID]
LEFT JOIN [SEGMENTO] AS [s] ON [g].[SEGMENTO] = [s].[ID]
INNER JOIN [CUENTA] AS [c] ON [g0].[IDCUENTA] = [c].[ID]
WHERE [p].[ID] = @__idproyecto_0
ORDER BY CASE
    WHEN ([g].[ESTADO] <> 'Forecast') OR [g].[ESTADO] IS NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END, [g].[FECHA]

SELECT [g].[ID] AS [IdGastosReal], [g].[IDGASTO] AS [IdGasto], [g].[IDPROVEEDOR] AS [IdProveedor], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[ID]
    ELSE 0
END AS [IdSegmento], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[NOMBRE]
    ELSE ''
END AS [NombreSegmento], [c].[CUENTA] AS [Cuenta], [c].[IDCUENTA] AS [IdCuenta], [g].[MONTO] AS [Monto], [g].[FECHA] AS [Fecha], [g].[OBSERVACION] AS [Observacion], [g].[ESTADO] AS [Estado], [g].[VENTA] AS [Venta]
FROM [PROYECTO] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [GASTOSEJECUCION] AS [g] ON [p].[ID] = [g].[IDPROYECTO]
INNER JOIN [GASTOS] AS [g0] ON [g].[IDGASTO] = [g0].[ID]
LEFT JOIN [SEGMENTO] AS [s] ON [g].[SEGMENTO] = [s].[ID]
INNER JOIN [CUENTA] AS [c] ON [g0].[IDCUENTA] = [c].[ID]
WHERE [p].[ID] = @__idproyecto_0
ORDER BY CASE
    WHEN ([g].[ESTADO] <> 'Forecast') OR [g].[ESTADO] IS NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END, [g].[FECHA]

SELECT [g].[ID] AS [IdGastosReal], [g].[IDGASTO] AS [IdGasto], [g].[IDPROVEEDOR] AS [IdProveedor], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[ID]
    ELSE 0
END AS [IdSegmento], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[NOMBRE]
    ELSE ''
END AS [NombreSegmento], [c].[CUENTA] AS [Cuenta], [c].[IDCUENTA] AS [IdCuenta], [g].[MONTO] AS [Monto], [g].[FECHA] AS [Fecha], [g].[OBSERVACION] AS [Observacion], [g].[ESTADO] AS [Estado], [g].[VENTA] AS [Venta]
FROM [PROYECTO] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [GASTOSEJECUCION] AS [g] ON [p].[ID] = [g].[IDPROYECTO]
INNER JOIN [GASTOS] AS [g0] ON [g].[IDGASTO] = [g0].[ID]
LEFT JOIN [SEGMENTO] AS [s] ON [g].[SEGMENTO] = [s].[ID]
INNER JOIN [CUENTA] AS [c] ON [g0].[IDCUENTA] = [c].[ID]
WHERE [p].[ID] = @__idproyecto_0
ORDER BY CASE
    WHEN ([g].[ESTADO] <> 'Forecast') OR [g].[ESTADO] IS NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END, [g].[FECHA]

SELECT [g].[ID] AS [IdGastosReal], [g].[IDGASTO] AS [IdGasto], [g].[IDPROVEEDOR] AS [IdProveedor], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[ID]
    ELSE 0
END AS [IdSegmento], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[NOMBRE]
    ELSE ''
END AS [NombreSegmento], [c].[CUENTA] AS [Cuenta], [c].[IDCUENTA] AS [IdCuenta], [g].[MONTO] AS [Monto], [g].[FECHA] AS [Fecha], [g].[OBSERVACION] AS [Observacion], [g].[ESTADO] AS [Estado], [g].[VENTA] AS [Venta]
FROM [PROYECTO] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [GASTOSEJECUCION] AS [g] ON [p].[ID] = [g].[IDPROYECTO]
INNER JOIN [GASTOS] AS [g0] ON [g].[IDGASTO] = [g0].[ID]
LEFT JOIN [SEGMENTO] AS [s] ON [g].[SEGMENTO] = [s].[ID]
INNER JOIN [CUENTA] AS [c] ON [g0].[IDCUENTA] = [c].[ID]
WHERE [p].[ID] = @__idproyecto_0
ORDER BY CASE
    WHEN ([g].[ESTADO] <> 'Forecast') OR [g].[ESTADO] IS NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END, [g].[FECHA]

SELECT [g].[ID] AS [IdGastosReal], [g].[IDGASTO] AS [IdGasto], [g].[IDPROVEEDOR] AS [IdProveedor], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[ID]
    ELSE 0
END AS [IdSegmento], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[NOMBRE]
    ELSE ''
END AS [NombreSegmento], [c].[CUENTA] AS [Cuenta], [c].[IDCUENTA] AS [IdCuenta], [g].[MONTO] AS [Monto], [g].[FECHA] AS [Fecha], [g].[OBSERVACION] AS [Observacion], [g].[ESTADO] AS [Estado], [g].[VENTA] AS [Venta]
FROM [PROYECTO] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [GASTOSEJECUCION] AS [g] ON [p].[ID] = [g].[IDPROYECTO]
INNER JOIN [GASTOS] AS [g0] ON [g].[IDGASTO] = [g0].[ID]
LEFT JOIN [SEGMENTO] AS [s] ON [g].[SEGMENTO] = [s].[ID]
INNER JOIN [CUENTA] AS [c] ON [g0].[IDCUENTA] = [c].[ID]
WHERE [p].[ID] = @__idproyecto_0
ORDER BY CASE
    WHEN ([g].[ESTADO] <> 'Forecast') OR [g].[ESTADO] IS NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END, [g].[FECHA]

SELECT [g].[ID] AS [IdGastosReal], [g].[IDGASTO] AS [IdGasto], [g].[IDPROVEEDOR] AS [IdProveedor], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[ID]
    ELSE 0
END AS [IdSegmento], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[NOMBRE]
    ELSE ''
END AS [NombreSegmento], [c].[CUENTA] AS [Cuenta], [c].[IDCUENTA] AS [IdCuenta], [g].[MONTO] AS [Monto], [g].[FECHA] AS [Fecha], [g].[OBSERVACION] AS [Observacion], [g].[ESTADO] AS [Estado], [g].[VENTA] AS [Venta]
FROM [PROYECTO] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [GASTOSEJECUCION] AS [g] ON [p].[ID] = [g].[IDPROYECTO]
INNER JOIN [GASTOS] AS [g0] ON [g].[IDGASTO] = [g0].[ID]
LEFT JOIN [SEGMENTO] AS [s] ON [g].[SEGMENTO] = [s].[ID]
INNER JOIN [CUENTA] AS [c] ON [g0].[IDCUENTA] = [c].[ID]
WHERE [p].[ID] = @__idproyecto_0
ORDER BY CASE
    WHEN ([g].[ESTADO] <> 'Forecast') OR [g].[ESTADO] IS NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END, [g].[FECHA]

2025-08-05 15:20:02.628 -04:00 [INF] Entity Framework Core 6.0.0 initialized 'PROYECTO_CONTROL_HORASContext' using provider 'Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.SqlServer:6.0.0' with options: None
2025-08-05 15:20:02.663 -04:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (16ms) [Parameters=[@__idproyecto_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [g].[ID] AS [IdGastosReal], [g].[IDGASTO] AS [IdGasto], [g].[IDPROVEEDOR] AS [IdProveedor], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[ID]
    ELSE 0
END AS [IdSegmento], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[NOMBRE]
    ELSE ''
END AS [NombreSegmento], [c].[CUENTA] AS [Cuenta], [c].[IDCUENTA] AS [IdCuenta], [g].[MONTO] AS [Monto], [g].[FECHA] AS [Fecha], [g].[OBSERVACION] AS [Observacion], [g].[ESTADO] AS [Estado], [g].[VENTA] AS [Venta]
FROM [PROYECTO] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [GASTOSEJECUCION] AS [g] ON [p].[ID] = [g].[IDPROYECTO]
INNER JOIN [GASTOS] AS [g0] ON [g].[IDGASTO] = [g0].[ID]
LEFT JOIN [SEGMENTO] AS [s] ON [g].[SEGMENTO] = [s].[ID]
INNER JOIN [CUENTA] AS [c] ON [g0].[IDCUENTA] = [c].[ID]
WHERE [p].[ID] = @__idproyecto_0
ORDER BY CASE
    WHEN ([g].[ESTADO] <> 'Forecast') OR [g].[ESTADO] IS NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)

SELECT [g].[ID] AS [IdGastosReal], [g].[IDGASTO] AS [IdGasto], [g].[IDPROVEEDOR] AS [IdProveedor], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[ID]
    ELSE 0
END AS [IdSegmento], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[NOMBRE]
    ELSE ''
END AS [NombreSegmento], [c].[CUENTA] AS [Cuenta], [c].[IDCUENTA] AS [IdCuenta], [g].[MONTO] AS [Monto], [g].[FECHA] AS [Fecha], [g].[OBSERVACION] AS [Observacion], [g].[ESTADO] AS [Estado], [g].[VENTA] AS [Venta]
FROM [PROYECTO] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [GASTOSEJECUCION] AS [g] ON [p].[ID] = [g].[IDPROYECTO]
INNER JOIN [GASTOS] AS [g0] ON [g].[IDGASTO] = [g0].[ID]
LEFT JOIN [SEGMENTO] AS [s] ON [g].[SEGMENTO] = [s].[ID]
INNER JOIN [CUENTA] AS [c] ON [g0].[IDCUENTA] = [c].[ID]
WHERE [p].[ID] = @__idproyecto_0
ORDER BY CASE
    WHEN ([g].[ESTADO] <> 'Forecast') OR [g].[ESTADO] IS NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END, [g].[FECHA]

SELECT [g].[ID] AS [IdGastosReal], [g].[IDGASTO] AS [IdGasto], [g].[IDPROVEEDOR] AS [IdProveedor], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[ID]
    ELSE 0
END AS [IdSegmento], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[NOMBRE]
    ELSE ''
END AS [NombreSegmento], [c].[CUENTA] AS [Cuenta], [c].[IDCUENTA] AS [IdCuenta], [g].[MONTO] AS [Monto], [g].[FECHA] AS [Fecha], [g].[OBSERVACION] AS [Observacion], [g].[ESTADO] AS [Estado], [g].[VENTA] AS [Venta]
FROM [PROYECTO] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [GASTOSEJECUCION] AS [g] ON [p].[ID] = [g].[IDPROYECTO]
INNER JOIN [GASTOS] AS [g0] ON [g].[IDGASTO] = [g0].[ID]
LEFT JOIN [SEGMENTO] AS [s] ON [g].[SEGMENTO] = [s].[ID]
INNER JOIN [CUENTA] AS [c] ON [g0].[IDCUENTA] = [c].[ID]
WHERE [p].[ID] = @__idproyecto_0
ORDER BY CASE
    WHEN ([g].[ESTADO] <> 'Forecast') OR [g].[ESTADO] IS NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END, [g].[FECHA]

SELECT [g].[ID] AS [IdGastosReal], [g].[IDGASTO] AS [IdGasto], [g].[IDPROVEEDOR] AS [IdProveedor], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[ID]
    ELSE 0
END AS [IdSegmento], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[NOMBRE]
    ELSE ''
END AS [NombreSegmento], [c].[CUENTA] AS [Cuenta], [c].[IDCUENTA] AS [IdCuenta], [g].[MONTO] AS [Monto], [g].[FECHA] AS [Fecha], [g].[OBSERVACION] AS [Observacion], [g].[ESTADO] AS [Estado], [g].[VENTA] AS [Venta]
FROM [PROYECTO] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [GASTOSEJECUCION] AS [g] ON [p].[ID] = [g].[IDPROYECTO]
INNER JOIN [GASTOS] AS [g0] ON [g].[IDGASTO] = [g0].[ID]
LEFT JOIN [SEGMENTO] AS [s] ON [g].[SEGMENTO] = [s].[ID]
INNER JOIN [CUENTA] AS [c] ON [g0].[IDCUENTA] = [c].[ID]
WHERE [p].[ID] = @__idproyecto_0
ORDER BY CASE
    WHEN ([g].[ESTADO] <> 'Forecast') OR [g].[ESTADO] IS NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END, [g].[FECHA]

SELECT [g].[ID] AS [IdGastosReal], [g].[IDGASTO] AS [IdGasto], [g].[IDPROVEEDOR] AS [IdProveedor], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[ID]
    ELSE 0
END AS [IdSegmento], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[NOMBRE]
    ELSE ''
END AS [NombreSegmento], [c].[CUENTA] AS [Cuenta], [c].[IDCUENTA] AS [IdCuenta], [g].[MONTO] AS [Monto], [g].[FECHA] AS [Fecha], [g].[OBSERVACION] AS [Observacion], [g].[ESTADO] AS [Estado], [g].[VENTA] AS [Venta]
FROM [PROYECTO] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [GASTOSEJECUCION] AS [g] ON [p].[ID] = [g].[IDPROYECTO]
INNER JOIN [GASTOS] AS [g0] ON [g].[IDGASTO] = [g0].[ID]
LEFT JOIN [SEGMENTO] AS [s] ON [g].[SEGMENTO] = [s].[ID]
INNER JOIN [CUENTA] AS [c] ON [g0].[IDCUENTA] = [c].[ID]
WHERE [p].[ID] = @__idproyecto_0
ORDER BY CASE
    WHEN ([g].[ESTADO] <> 'Forecast') OR [g].[ESTADO] IS NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END, [g].[FECHA]

    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[ID]
    ELSE 0
END AS [IdSegmento], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[NOMBRE]
    ELSE ''
END AS [NombreSegmento], [c].[CUENTA] AS [Cuenta], [c].[IDCUENTA] AS [IdCuenta], [g].[MONTO] AS [Monto], [g].[FECHA] AS [Fecha], [g].[OBSERVACION] AS [Observacion], [g].[ESTADO] AS [Estado], [g].[VENTA] AS [Venta]
FROM [PROYECTO] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [GASTOSEJECUCION] AS [g] ON [p].[ID] = [g].[IDPROYECTO]
INNER JOIN [GASTOS] AS [g0] ON [g].[IDGASTO] = [g0].[ID]
LEFT JOIN [SEGMENTO] AS [s] ON [g].[SEGMENTO] = [s].[ID]
INNER JOIN [CUENTA] AS [c] ON [g0].[IDCUENTA] = [c].[ID]
WHERE [p].[ID] = @__idproyecto_0
ORDER BY CASE

    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END, [g].[FECHA]

SELECT [g].[ID] AS [IdGastosReal], [g].[IDGASTO] AS [IdGasto], [g].[IDPROVEEDOR] AS [IdProveedor], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[ID]
    ELSE 0
END AS [IdSegmento], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[NOMBRE]
    ELSE ''
END AS [NombreSegmento], [c].[CUENTA] AS [Cuenta], [c].[IDCUENTA] AS [IdCuenta], [g].[MONTO] AS [Monto], [g].[FECHA] AS [Fecha], [g].[OBSERVACION] AS [Observacion], [g].[ESTADO] AS [Estado], [g].[VENTA] AS [Venta]
FROM [PROYECTO] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [GASTOSEJECUCION] AS [g] ON [p].[ID] = [g].[IDPROYECTO]
INNER JOIN [GASTOS] AS [g0] ON [g].[IDGASTO] = [g0].[ID]
LEFT JOIN [SEGMENTO] AS [s] ON [g].[SEGMENTO] = [s].[ID]
INNER JOIN [CUENTA] AS [c] ON [g0].[IDCUENTA] = [c].[ID]
WHERE [p].[ID] = @__idproyecto_0
ORDER BY CASE
    WHEN ([g].[ESTADO] <> 'Forecast') OR [g].[ESTADO] IS NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END, [g].[FECHA]

    ELSE ''

SELECT [g].[ID] AS [IdGastosReal], [g].[IDGASTO] AS [IdGasto], [g].[IDPROVEEDOR] AS [IdProveedor], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[ID]
    ELSE 0
END AS [IdSegmento], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[NOMBRE]
    ELSE ''
END AS [NombreSegmento], [c].[CUENTA] AS [Cuenta], [c].[IDCUENTA] AS [IdCuenta], [g].[MONTO] AS [Monto], [g].[FECHA] AS [Fecha], [g].[OBSERVACION] AS [Observacion], [g].[ESTADO] AS [Estado], [g].[VENTA] AS [Venta]
FROM [PROYECTO] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [GASTOSEJECUCION] AS [g] ON [p].[ID] = [g].[IDPROYECTO]
INNER JOIN [GASTOS] AS [g0] ON [g].[IDGASTO] = [g0].[ID]
LEFT JOIN [SEGMENTO] AS [s] ON [g].[SEGMENTO] = [s].[ID]
INNER JOIN [CUENTA] AS [c] ON [g0].[IDCUENTA] = [c].[ID]
WHERE [p].[ID] = @__idproyecto_0
ORDER BY CASE
    WHEN ([g].[ESTADO] <> 'Forecast') OR [g].[ESTADO] IS NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END, [g].[FECHA]

SELECT [g].[ID] AS [IdGastosReal], [g].[IDGASTO] AS [IdGasto], [g].[IDPROVEEDOR] AS [IdProveedor], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[ID]
    ELSE 0
END AS [IdSegmento], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[NOMBRE]
    ELSE ''
END AS [NombreSegmento], [c].[CUENTA] AS [Cuenta], [c].[IDCUENTA] AS [IdCuenta], [g].[MONTO] AS [Monto], [g].[FECHA] AS [Fecha], [g].[OBSERVACION] AS [Observacion], [g].[ESTADO] AS [Estado], [g].[VENTA] AS [Venta]
FROM [PROYECTO] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [GASTOSEJECUCION] AS [g] ON [p].[ID] = [g].[IDPROYECTO]
INNER JOIN [GASTOS] AS [g0] ON [g].[IDGASTO] = [g0].[ID]
LEFT JOIN [SEGMENTO] AS [s] ON [g].[SEGMENTO] = [s].[ID]
INNER JOIN [CUENTA] AS [c] ON [g0].[IDCUENTA] = [c].[ID]
WHERE [p].[ID] = @__idproyecto_0
ORDER BY CASE
    WHEN ([g].[ESTADO] <> 'Forecast') OR [g].[ESTADO] IS NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END, [g].[FECHA]

INNER JOIN [SERVICIOS] AS [s0] ON [s].[IDSERVICIO] = [s0].[ID]

SELECT [s].[ID] AS [idservicioreal], [s].[IDSERVICIO], [s].[IDPROVEEDOR] AS [idproveedor], [c].[CUENTA], [c].[IDCUENTA], [s].[MONTO], [s].[FECHA], [s].[OBSERVACION] AS [observacion], [s].[ESTADO] AS [Estado], [s].[TIPOSERVICIO] AS [tipo]
FROM [PROYECTO] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [SERVICIOSEJECUCION] AS [s] ON [p].[ID] = [s].[IDPROYECTO]
INNER JOIN [SERVICIOS] AS [s0] ON [s].[IDSERVICIO] = [s0].[ID]
INNER JOIN [CUENTA] AS [c] ON [s0].[IDCUENTA] = [c].[ID]
WHERE ([p].[ID] = @__idproyecto_0) AND ([s].[TIPOSERVICIO] = @__tipo_1)
ORDER BY CASE
    WHEN ([s].[ESTADO] <> 'Forecast') OR [s].[ESTADO] IS NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END, [s].[FECHA]

SELECT [s].[ID] AS [idservicioreal], [s].[IDSERVICIO], [s].[IDPROVEEDOR] AS [idproveedor], [c].[CUENTA], [c].[IDCUENTA], [s].[MONTO], [s].[FECHA], [s].[OBSERVACION] AS [observacion], [s].[ESTADO] AS [Estado], [s].[TIPOSERVICIO] AS [tipo]
FROM [PROYECTO] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [SERVICIOSEJECUCION] AS [s] ON [p].[ID] = [s].[IDPROYECTO]
INNER JOIN [SERVICIOS] AS [s0] ON [s].[IDSERVICIO] = [s0].[ID]
INNER JOIN [CUENTA] AS [c] ON [s0].[IDCUENTA] = [c].[ID]
WHERE ([p].[ID] = @__idproyecto_0) AND ([s].[TIPOSERVICIO] = @__tipo_1)
ORDER BY CASE
    WHEN ([s].[ESTADO] <> 'Forecast') OR [s].[ESTADO] IS NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END, [s].[FECHA]

INNER JOIN [SERVICIOSEJECUCION] AS [s] ON [p].[ID] = [s].[IDPROYECTO]
INNER JOIN [SERVICIOS] AS [s0] ON [s].[IDSERVICIO] = [s0].[ID]

    WHEN ([s].[ESTADO] <> 'Forecast') OR [s].[ESTADO] IS NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
